casebody.data:
STATE of Missouri, Respondent,
v.
Kirstin A. STEPHENS, Appellant. WD 80230 Missouri Court of Appeals, Western District. ORDER FILED: April 3, 2018 Damien De Loyola, Kansas City, MO, Counsel for Appellant. Richard Starnes, Jefferson City, MO, Counsel for Respondent. Before Division Two: James Edward Welsh, P.J., Alok Ahuja, and Anthony Rex Gabbert, JJ.

ORDER

Per Curiam:

Kirstin A. Stephens appeals her convictions, following a jury trial, on one count of first-degree murder ( § 565.020, RSMo ) and one count of armed criminal action ( § 571.015, RSMo ). We affirm. Rule 30.25(b).
